## Steps to reproduce

Running the following test class fails with an

> ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: Index 1 out of bounds for length 1

```java
@ParameterizedClass
@ValueSource(ints = 1)
class NotEnoughArgumentsForFieldsTestCase {

	@Parameter(0)
